SnArcInfo

public SnArcInfo(java.lang.String key,
                 java.lang.String net,
                 java.lang.String fromNode,
                 java.lang.String toNode)
Creates an arc. The cost, upper bound and flow of the arc are set to zero.
Parameters:
key - the name of the arc
net - the name of the network containing the arc
fromNode - the name of the node from which the arc starts
toNode - the name of the node to which the arc ends
